expression: body
---
Read or write configuration values. (Hermes parity: `hermes config`.)

Usage: config <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list  Print every configured key and its current value
  get   Read a single configuration key
  set   Write a single configuration key
  path  Print the path of the active `gaussclaw.toml`
  help  Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
